                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Until it acts, the taxidermy allosaurus resembles an ordinary (if well-crafted) taxidermy creature. It has an automatic result of 43 on Deception checks and DCs to pass as an ordinary taxidermy display.</p>"
                },
