        {
            "_id": "XAp5croNuhYxOEyY",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Thrashing Tail",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The taxidermy allosaurus smashes furniture and displays in the area with its tail, spreading the resulting rubble around. A 5-foot by 15-foot area of your choice that has at least one square adjacent to the creature becomes difficult terrain. If this area includes the stone tub, the acid splashes out and the difficult terrain becomes hazardous terrain as well that deals @Damage[1d6[acid]] damage.</p>"
                },
